p.e:
WHAT IS THIS PLACE?

A PLACE TO EASILY ONE-BUTTON-EQUIP
BASE AVATAR TEMPLATES.

ONCE YOU FOLLOW THE STEPS AT THE
ENTRANCE, YOU CAN MIX & MATCH ANY
BODY PARTS INSIDE INSTANTLY!


ALL BODY PARTS INSIDE ARE CLONEABLE,
YOU CAN PUT THEM IN YOUR INVENTORY, 
TAKE THEM HOME AND CUSTOMIZE THEM,
BUILD ONTO THEM, OR USE THE
RECTANGLUAR TEMPLATES AS YOUR BASE.
